CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 21, reads: "7. Krey salesman, J.H. Savery, presents a salad set to winner, Bessie Mills"
TitMainTitle: J.H. Savery, presenting a salad set to Bessie Mills, standing in front of cooking demonstration display with Jessie Vann, in Syria Mosque for the Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
